{"id":3088,"date":"2024-01-02T15:23:32","date_gmt":"2021-02-02T09:53:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=3088"},"modified":"2023-05-08T14:03:27","modified_gmt":"2023-05-08T08:33:27","slug":"romantic-bedroom-interior-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/romantic-bedroom-interior-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"A Room Full Of Love! 10 Ways To Design A Romantic Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"When was the last time you watched&nbsp;<em>The Notebook<\/em>&nbsp;and wondered if someone could build an elegant house for you just like Noah built one for Allie? Or if your spouse granted you full freedom to design your nest just the way Christian did with Anastasia? Well, it doesn\u2019t happen in real life, does it?\n\nDesigning your bedroom once you are married can be challenging, considering that your room\u2019s aesthetics must reflect both your personas. When married, you not only share a bed but each corner of the bedroom with your spouse. From the walls to cupboards,&nbsp; sheets to rugs, colours to room decor \u2013 your spouse and you need to fall in love with everything in your bedroom.\n\nDo remember, your bedroom holds the honour of being the most special place in your home. Defined by four walls, it is the space where you dream your future together. It\u2019s where your spouse and you spend quality time, right? So bring out the most romantic version of yourself as you design your bedroom. It has to be comfortable, elegant, impeccable and intimate.\n\nThere are lots of parameters to consider before you get started. This includes the size and shape of your room, your personal styles, colour preferences, budget, furnishings, and other tiny details that generally skip our mind. It is always a good idea to hire an interior designer as you begin this mammoth task because they hold a creative lens.\n\nJust to get you started we have compiled ten dreamy design ideas for your bedroom to keep the romance alive. We bet these designs will excite you. And once your bedroom is all set, you won\u2019t want to step out of your cosy little nest, even over a long weekend! Let\u2019s get on a design trip together and get started, shall we?\n<h2>Get Cheeky With Pillows!<\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_3120\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3120\" style=\"width: 820px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3120\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Romantic bedrooms design with cheeky with pillows these big soft pillows with smaller ones is perfect bedroom designs for couples\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054424\/cheeky-with-pillows-for-romantic-bedroom-design-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3120\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">How many pillows are too many when it comes to making your room cosy?<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/figure>\nRedefine the term pillow talk! There\u2019s something sexy about pillows in a bedroom. A perfect combination of big soft pillows with smaller ones is perfect for a cosy snuggle. White linen on pillows with embroidery are ideal for a classic traditional bedroom and lend a pretty, pristine look.\n\n<strong>Design idea<\/strong>: Avoid playing too many colours while picking pillows and cushions. Stick to classic linen feather-like white and pastel colours with matching spreads. Just don\u2019t forget the softness!\n<h2>Candles And Flowers, Never Go Wrong<\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_3119\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3119\" style=\"width: 820px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3119\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples.jpg\" alt=\"Romantic bedroom ideas for couples with candles and flowers for makes romantic bedrooms\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054425\/candles-and-flowers-for-romantic-bedrooms-for-couples-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3119\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Infuse fragrances into your bedroom with essential oil diffusers, pillow mists, and scented candles<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/figure>\nBring back that honeymoon suite feel to your bedroom. There\u2019s no doubt, hotel rooms that brim with fresh and calming scents offer a different level of luxury. You can add the same charm to your bedroom. A serene, scent-misted bedroom will calm your senses (and of your partner!). Light up your room well with scented candles for a romantic night in with some take-away dinner.\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n<strong>Design idea:<\/strong>&nbsp;Rosewater and scented candles are refreshing and send out relaxing vibes. When opting for the latter, pick beautiful canisters to bring in an artistic edge to your scented paradise. Choose aromatic varieties that offer a pleasant, understated scent. You can also add essential oil diffusers or pillow mists to infuse fragrance into your bedroom.\n<h2>Build Yourself A Cocoon<\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_3121\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3121\" style=\"width: 820px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3121\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples.jpg\" alt=\"Couple bedroom design by reinforce a sense of privacy and intimacy with this cocoon\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054423\/cocoon-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-couples-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3121\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reinforce a sense of privacy and intimacy with this cocoon-like setting<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/figure>\nYes! You heard it right. Build yourself a cocoon. Well, not literally a cocoon but a cosy little corner where you feel protected relaxed from hum-drum of everyday life. Add a pile of sheets and sheers with some really soft pillows. Voila! There you have your cocoon. Sneak in a snuggle or two on a lazy Sunday afternoon!\n\n<strong>Design idea:<\/strong>&nbsp;Drape curtains in front of your bed for solitude and intimacy. It\u2019ll feel like a tiny cocoon one that is cut off from the outside world. Fluffy bedding you\u2019d never wish to get off doesn\u2019t harm either.\n\nAlso Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/romantic-bedroom-colors\/\">Romantic Bedroom Colours For Your Home<\/a>\n<h2>Add A Luxe Headboard<\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_3125\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3125\" style=\"width: 820px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3125\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms.jpg\" alt=\"Romantic bedroom ideas for married couples with green velvet headboard to make more romantic bedrooms\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054418\/green-velvet-headboard-romantic-couple-bedrooms-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3125\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">That luxe green velvet headboard elicits the romance of a deep forest<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/figure>\nA luxe velvet headboard elicits the romance of a garden or a deep forest. A headboard, one in a vibrant hue, lends a subtle touch if you are looking for something less overtly romantic.\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n<strong>Design idea:&nbsp;<\/strong>Carefully select the colour and size of your headboard as it can lower the charm of your bedroom if not in proportion. A velvet-textured headboard in a deep shade works magically well of it goes with the rest of your decor.\n<h2>Hang A Canopy<\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_3124\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3124\" style=\"width: 820px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3124\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples.jpg\" alt=\"A beautiful canopy paired with flowers lends a chic touch to your romantic master bedroom design\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054419\/flowery-canop-romantic-bedroom-ideas-for-married-couples-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3124\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Is there anything more sensual than a flowery canopy?<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/figure>\nCanopies are sexy. Yes, there\u2019s just something mysterious and enchanting about its soft, flowy and translucent look. It offers you privacy yet keeps the mystery going. A beautiful canopy paired with flowers lends a chic touch to your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom design<\/a>. But of course, real flowers must be restricted to special occasions, if you know what we mean!\n\n<strong>Design idea:<\/strong>&nbsp;Pick the right set of sheer fabrics and punch things up with splashes of pastel coloured pillows and rugs.\n<h2>Stay Grounded In Your Romantic Bedroom<\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_3129\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3129\" style=\"width: 820px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3129\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms.jpg\" alt=\"Hite linens, soft comforters and lots of pillows is always the right choice for romantic bedroom design\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054415\/stay-grounded-in-romantic-bedrooms-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3129\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">This room is an uncomplicated setting for a couple in love with life<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/figure>\nFloor-level bedding sets the mood for sexy fun. Loose white linens, soft comforters and lots of pillows is always the right choice. The ease and comfort this bed offers is irresistible. Perfect for chilly evenings and a cup of coffee!\n\n<strong>Design idea:&nbsp;<\/strong>Be picky while choosing your mattress. An incredibly soft bed might be appealing but is not ideal for sleeping. Play with colours as long as it doesn\u2019t disturb the mood of your bedroom. Hint: Softer pastels are a good choice!\n<h2>Delicate Curtains Are Sublime<\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_3123\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3123\" style=\"width: 820px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3123\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom ideas for couples with soft and delicate sheers with the right amount of lighting\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054420\/delicate-curtains-in-bedroom-designs-for-couples-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3123\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Soft and delicate sheers with the right amount of lighting are nothing short of perfect<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/figure>\nSemi-sheer, transparent curtains elicit a sense of ethereal romance. They scatter light for a delicate and surreal effect. Even better if your bed looks out to a picturesque scene when the curtains are pulled back.\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n<strong>Design idea:<\/strong>&nbsp;Try to choose solid white or neutral coloured sheers in a soft fabric. Prints or deep colours can dim the romantic vibe of your bedroom.\n<h2>Come On Baby Light My Fire<\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_3128\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3128\" style=\"width: 820px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3128\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054416\/romantic-master-bedroom-ideas-with-fireplace.jpg\" alt=\"Romantic bedrooms with an indoor fireplace will kindle the passion and closed fireplace with glass or iron cabinets looks much nicer\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/17054416\/romantic-master-bedroom-ideas-with-fireplace.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/